EzBu&_nc_ht=scontent.oculuscdn.com&_nc_gid=AUvpi6StLukF-XjZeTAVnY1&oh=00_AYBTs5A0wJVrvxLxyqNriDuiV-RoZLBipGZUHYKriOZ2tw&oe=66F6A940"}, {"file_name": "HighresScreenshot00004.png", "id": "1123322065406156", "uri": "https://scontent.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/75451778_1123322068739489_4045797699526063494_n.png?_nc_cat=110&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=GRLWaPrsMv0Q7kNvgH8Tnp-&_nc_ht=scontent.oculuscdn.com&_nc_gid=AUvpi6StLukF-XjZeTAVnY1&oh=00_AYATE8KEX88PJnyceCGxmZ_OXY5IwzlaB7ee56X6O6qXEQ&oe=66F69E02"}, {"file_name": "HighresScreenshot00002.png", "id": "1142596546674219", "uri": "https://scontent.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/75485580_1142596550007552_772410991094174589_n.png?_nc_cat=111&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=5obvXkGnIukQ7kNvgGD6H5Z&_nc_ht=scontent.oculuscdn.com&_nc_gid=AUvpi6StLukF-XjZeTAVnY1&oh=00_AYD-yxLU5OdoU6ripab3VDFazzsdVCpmI4wAHXJUIU0Efw&oe=66F6876E"}, {"file_name": "HighresScreenshot00006.png", "id": "7550646221654282", "uri": "https://scontent.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/38974733_7550646228320948_1826245149111678906_n.png?_nc_cat=101&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=2uSjejOIgQcQ7kNvgEvNNth&_nc_ht=scontent.oculuscdn.com&_nc_gid=AUvpi6StLukF-XjZeTAVnY1&oh=00_AYDust34QgUWVt3e9o2yTkN-pR9qqz46NzaDz4iIwYdPVw&oe=66F695A7"}, {"file_name": "HighresScreenshot00005.png", "id": "919243899714398", "uri": "https://scontent.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/38982696_919243919714396_6860426524042517358_n.png?_nc_cat=109&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=GMXP50IGAvgQ7kNvgHFLoNw&_nc_ht=scontent.oculuscdn.com&_nc_gid=AUvpi6StLukF-XjZeTAVnY1&oh=00_AYCJchejHWqJTsSoKbdGht1NpAkmBG_Q_SYGe6k83ILDbw&oe=66F69617"}], "video_trailer": null, "video_trailer_thumbnail": {"file_name": "videocover.png", "id": "1856125128361075", "uri": "https://scontent.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/39035403_1856125131694408_3239532312285045631_n.png?_nc_cat=111&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=coZ-4BXCJ8gQ7kNvgECG43y&_nc_ht=scontent.oculuscdn.com&_nc_gid=AUvpi6StLukF-XjZeTAVnY1&oh=00_AYC0ju7cz5lzLZAxEJSshU6l9jpxImCwsorqlLeRSPkurw&oe=66F68833"}, "display_name": "AI Therapist: Your Emotional Guide", "keywords": [], "long_description": "Welcome to AI Therapist: Your Emotional Guide, an innovative journey into emotional well-being powered by artificial intelligence. This app bridges technology and human emotions, enabling users to have natural and meaningful conversations with a generative AI therapist that responds with understanding and relevance.\n\nAI Therapist provides a non-judgmental space for individuals to explore their feelings, thoughts, and emotions. Whether seeking reflection, support, or new ways to connect with your inner self, AI Therapist delivers realistic interactions for a deeper understanding of emotions.\n\nKey Features:\n\n\u2022 Immersive 3D interface for engaging therapy sessions.\n\u2022 Realistic AI conversations for emotional support.\n\u2022 A safe platform for self-discovery and growth.\n\u2022 Perfect for daily check-ins, with an AI that offers effective assistance.\n\nNote: AI Therapist is experimental and not a substitute for professional therapy. It represents a step towards leveraging AI for emotional well-being, offering companionship on the path to self-improvement.", "short_description": "Explore emotions with AI: AI Therapist: Your Emotional Guide offers innovative therapy sessions with generative AI for emotional self-discovery. Experience natural conversations where the AI understands and guides you through your feelings, creating a unique space for emotional exploration."}]}, "developer_name": null, "developer_privacy_policy_url": "https://doc-hosting.flycricket.io/ai-therapist-your-emotional-guide-privacy-policy/2d3288f3-8fd3-4db4-9fdb-8ef6efb526a3/privacy", "developer_terms_of_service_url": null, "publisher_name": "Raetae Studios", "support_website_url": null, "website_url": "http://aitherapist.rf.gd/", "category": null, "comfort_rating": "NOT_RATED", "comfort_tags": [], "context_category": {"id": "362692211442873", "context_category": 